title: UPCOMING UNITS OUTDOOR LOUNGE AREA HEAT AND AC/NEAR DOWNTOWN
posting_body: ['Welcome to Pleasanton Glen Apartment Homes!', 'Our apartments for rent in Pleasanton, CA are a hop and skip from major employers, main streets and the 580 and 680 freeways.', 'Have to take someone to school on the way?', 'You will be happy to know that our schools have a high ranking and are on the California Distinguished School list!', 'Plus, they are super close by.', '- Three sparkling pools with sun decks', '- Relaxing covered spa', '- Outdoor lounge area', '- Fully equipped fitness center', '- Beautiful courtyards with mature landscaping', '- Assigned covered parking', '- Extra rentable storage on-site', '- 24-hour laundry center', '- On-site friendly and professional management and maintenance team', '- Blocks from historical Downtown', '- Easy access to Bart, ACE Train, I-680 and I-580', '- Near major Tri-Valley employment centers, shopping, dining & entertainment', '- Award winning Pleasanton school district', '- 24-Hour parcel locker room', '- Many options to pay rent including, credit card, on-line and ACH', '- Resident referral program', '- Flexible 3-12 month lease terms (additional fees may apply for shorter terms)', '- Heat and AC', '- Large closets and storage spaces', '- Granite countertops in kitchen & bathrooms', '- Full kitchen Whirlpool stainless steel appliance package', '- In-home front-loading washer and dryer', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>', 'Pricing is subject to change.', 'Call for details.']
